                    </AccordionToggle>
            </Heading>
        </CollapseHeader>
        <CollapseBody>
                <p>This privacy notice provides information regarding how Theradex Oncology processes the personal information collected or received both from visitors to our website www.theradex.com and from our customers and suppliers during our business. </p>
